{{作品名稱|name=''New Year's Eve''|hk=緣滿除夕夜|tw=101次新年快樂|cn=新年前夜}}是2011年上映的一部浪漫喜劇電影，由[[蓋瑞·馬歇爾|蓋瑞·馬歇爾]]導演。這部電影的很多演員和工作人員都和2010年電影《[[情人節快樂|情人節快樂]]》的陣容相同，但并不是《情人節快樂》的續篇，而是獨立的故事。這部電影還拍攝了紐約時代廣場上百萬人倒數慶祝新年的畫面<ref name="ew-biel-joins">{{cite web | date = 2010-12-08 | author = Josh Rottenberg | url = http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/12/08/jessica-biel-new-years-eve/ | title = Jessica Biel joins the cast of 'New Year's Eve' | quote = Biel also appeared in Valentine’s Day but, since New Year’s Eve is not a sequel to that film, she will be playing a new character in an entirely different storyline | work = [[エンターテインメント・ウィークリー|Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher = [[:en:Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]] | accessdate = 2011-05-24 | archive-date = 2014-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141105152430/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2010/12/08/jessica-biel-new-years-eve/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=72444<!-- the real source though is below but likely to get stuck behind a paywall -->http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sarah-jessica-parker-joining-years-60236 {{Wayback|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sarah-jessica-parker-joining-years-60236 |date=20210126023030 }}</ref>。

==劇情==
本片全数于纽约实景拍摄，叙述新年的前一天除夕，不论形单影只还是成双成对的男男女女，在新年前夕的纽约里交织出了颂扬爱、希望、宽恕和第二次机会及重新开始的浪漫喜剧。

